{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903190/extras/WISHLISTNOW.png?t=1730114636\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903190/extras/KeyFoundations.png?t=1730114636\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903190/extras/maverick_store_page_divider_open.png?t=1730114636\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maverick is a 2D action platformer metroidvania, drawing inspiration from fan-favorite SNES classics - such as Megaman X, Metroid, and Castlevania. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Modernization and quality of life that you would expect</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tight and accessible controls - emphasized across all movement, jumping, and abilities </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Regions with unique style, eye-catching rooms, and memorable landmarks  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meaningful progression with an emphasis on player volition</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903190/extras/Maverick_GIF_Action.gif?t=1730114636\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903190/extras/Maverick_GIF_Action2.gif?t=1730114636\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903190/extras/GameFeatures.png?t=1730114636\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903190/extras/maverick_store_page_divider_open.png?t=1730114636\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Evolve your Xeno-Armor with enhancements to your Head, Body, Legs, and Arms  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight dynamic and challenging bosses, mini-bosses, and enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore an interconnected world with interesting mechanics and unique points of interest</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock fast-travel points for convenient traversal</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903190/extras/Maverick_GIF_Action3.gif?t=1730114636\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903190/extras/Maverick_GIF_UpgradeScreen.gif?t=1730114636\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903190/extras/Story_Setting.png?t=1730114636\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903190/extras/maverick_store_page_divider_open.png?t=1730114636\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In 2070 or so, information and communication is limited.  What\u2019s left of humanity is enslaved or in hiding.  The human resistance holds tightly onto operations close to an alien-android gateway.  The lab where project maverick has unfolded is under attack, and you\u2019re about to wake up earlier than expected.  Uncover your past,  meet friends and foes along your journey, and unravel the mysteries of project maverick and the xeno metal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903190/extras/Envi